OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 17 Jul to Sun 26 JulFA
OL,6,Fchange in weather pattern is likely by
OL,7,Fthe start of this period, with the
OL,8,Fpreceding dry and sunny weather
OL,9,Fbreaking down into a more unsettled
OL,10,Fspell. Some heavy and thundery showers
OL,11,Fare likely, particularly across the
OL,12,Fsouth of the UK. Into the following
OL,13,Fweek, a short spell of more settled
OL,14,Fweather is likely at first, before
OL,15,Fmore changeable conditions return
OL,16,Flater. This brings showers or longer
OL,17,Fspells of rain at times, perhaps heavy
OL,18,Fand thundery in places. Temperatures
OL,19,Fare likely to be above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
